{"id":499044,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michel_Piccoli","text":"Michel Piccoli (27 December 1925 \u2013 12 May 2020) was a French actor, director, singer, musician, and screenwriter. He was known for his roles in \"Belle de Jour\", \"Atlantic City\", \"La Belle Noiseuse\", and in \"We Have a Pope\". Piccoli was born in Paris, France.\nPiccoli died on 12 May 2020 in Cannes of a stroke, aged 94.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"France","surface_form":"French","offset":54},{"uri":"Actor","surface_form":"actor","offset":61},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"director","offset":68},{"uri":"Singer","surface_form":"singer","offset":78},{"uri":"Musician","surface_form":"musician","offset":86},{"uri":"Screenwriter","surface_form":"screenwriter","offset":100},{"uri":"Belle_de_Jour","surface_form":"Belle de Jour","offset":145},{"uri":"Atlantic_City_(movie)","surface_form":"Atlantic City","offset":162},{"uri":"La_Belle_Noiseuse","surface_form":"La Belle Noiseuse","offset":179},{"uri":"We_Have_a_Pope","surface_form":"We Have a Pope","offset":207},{"uri":"Paris","surface_form":"Paris","offset":244},{"uri":"Cannes","surface_form":"Cannes","offset":290},{"uri":"Stroke","surface_form":"stroke","offset":302}]}